aa(lp119
VBut I nonetheless emerged and relapsed,
p120
aVand emerged and relapsed,
p121
aVand emerged and relapsed,
p122
aVand finally understood
p123
aVI would have to be on medication and in therapy forever.
p124
aVAnd I thought,
p125
aV"But is it a chemical problem or a psychological problem?
p126
aVAnd does it need a chemical cure or a philosophical cure?"
p127
aVAnd I couldn't figure out which it was.
p128
aVAnd then I understood that actually,
p129
aVwe aren't advanced enough in either area for it to explain things fully.
p130
aVThe chemical cure and the psychological cure
p131
aVboth have a role to play,
p132
aVand I also figured out that depression was something
p133
aVthat was braided so deep into us
p134
aVthat there was no separating it from our character and personality.
