aa(lp136
VI want to say that the treatments we have for depression are appalling.
p137
aVThey're not very effective.
p138
aVThey're extremely costly.
p139
aVThey come with innumerable side effects.
p140
aVThey're a disaster.
p141
aVBut I am so grateful that I live now and not 50 years ago,
p142
aVwhen there would have been almost nothing to be done.
p143
aVI hope that 50 years hence,
p144
aVpeople will hear about my treatments
p145
aVand be appalled that anyone endured such primitive science.
